{"tid":687302,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「巴打入」男朋友重視其他人多過自己同好自私","createTime":"2018-06-02T06:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T08:19:02.000Z","uid":22244,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e816280a7d8269e01b355d2985abf4ab0f95d69e","tid":687302,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人男朋友重視其他人多過自己，<br />\n例如朋友，佢個妹，<br />\n佢返工期間，成日上線都唔應我whatsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我問佢點解唔應我，佢話好忙<br />\n之後俾我發現全日係到同d朋友傾whatsapp<br />\n入都冇入過我個chat冇藍剔我，但有上過線<br />\n<br />\n仲有如果我同佢個妹同時叫佢<br />\n佢一定會應左佢妹先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d咩野佢買左返黎但多餘冇用放係屋企，<br />\n我會話不如俾我拎返去屋企俾屋企人用，<br />\n佢就唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢呀妹話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：呀哥，我想拎去用呀，佢就話好呀拎去啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有，出去食飯，成日話自己好窮要我俾<br />\n上網睇中d咩都叫我用信用卡幫佢碌<br />\n但同佢呀妹出街，呀妹叫佢請，就仆住去請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟我係佢心目中係重唔重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04c9f6d3610588f7cc1828794d24ecd6322e3f4","tid":687302,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:44:13.000Z","msg":"屌你個妹控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ac024234d975d956e519f4803fb039e40e9bd8","tid":687302,"uid":144776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13af8811d39ce0b49ead219de1f5dea74f3e5e32","tid":687302,"uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"可能你冇被佢屌 個妹有所以先厚此薄彼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d538cd3fe1783f684436b012ad0e2869f0fe85ad","tid":687302,"uid":32765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"repl